These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Flower: lily, marigold, tulip, begonia
Transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. Flower:begonia is on the left of Flower:lily##1
2. Flower:lily is on the right of Flower:begonia##1
3. Transport:car is on the far left or far right##3
4. Flower:tulip is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
5. Transport:roller is between Transport:car and Transport:motorbike##2
6. Flower:begonia == Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Flower   | begonia | lily     | tulip | marigold |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
Food: corn, lemon, nectarine, cranberry
Transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. Food:lemon is on the left of Transport:helicopter##1
2. Transport:trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. Food:cranberry is on the left of Transport:trike##1
4. Transport:trike is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1
5. Food:nectarine is on the far right##1
6. Transport:bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Food   | corn | lemon    | cranberry     | nectarine  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

