.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
Music-Genre: house, jazz, pop, rock
House: colonial, gothic-revival, cottage, art-deco
1. House:art-deco is on the left or right of Music-Genre:jazz##3
2. Music-Genre:jazz is on the far left##1
3. House:cottage is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1
4. House:colonial is on the left or right of Music-Genre:house##3
5. House:cottage is on the right of Music-Genre:pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| House           | gothic-revival | art-deco | cottage | colonial  |

