.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
Pet: turtle, rat, hedgehog, pony
Nationality: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. Nationality:indian is on the left of Pet:hedgehog##1
2. Pet:pony is between Pet:turtle and Nationality:egyptian##2
3. Pet:pony is on the left or right of Pet:hedgehog##3
4. Nationality:egyptian is on the left or right of Nationality:indian##3
5. Pet:turtle is on the right of Pet:rat##1
6. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Pet         | rat | turtle | pony | hedgehog  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

